{
  "stem": "2460.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we-- we had strong feelings that, yes, they are taking us somewhere into a-- relocate, to relocate us deep in Hungaria.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we were sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My-- the father, I remember, told us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the-- the-- the train made certain unusual turns from Levice to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then from Budapest back to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know why it's making all those routes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I know that's because the railroads were bombed all over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we thought that maybe they are looking for the right place for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in June '44, the Jewish community still didn't know that there were gas chambers and--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only when we crossed the Slovakian and Polish border-- my father was well-traveled, like I said-- we heard trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- he saw the Polish name from a town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember he was looking out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, we are in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole 50 people, we started to cry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was to us, something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What we are doing in Poland?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe then they understand, the older people, that those stories that the little children told us-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this-- this is the-- this is the story.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why, otherwise, would take us to Poland?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all the horror stories that they were not telling us children, but they knew about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Probably then they realized that those are the true stories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you know what the town was that your father saw?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember the name, because it had no significance for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the train crossed the border, my father said that he's sorry that we didn't run away because we had a-- we were offered to ran away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
